title: Birdcall EDA: Chirp, Hoot and Flutter
description: Birds! Birds come in so many varieties of colours, shapes, sizes... and voices? Humans are quite adept at recognizing each other's voices and so are ML models now. But how good are ML models in recognizing voices of bird species in their natural habitat along with the sounds of nature? We will have an answer to it at the end of this competition.
